schools.name: Young Women's Leadership Academy at Arnold

data.description:
Wow! Must see highly customized large updated 2 story with a brand new above ground pool for those hot summer days! Recent high efficiency AC units, Sub Zero refrigerator, Oversized bedrooms, Jetted tubs in two bathrooms, two laundry areas, wet bar in upstairs game room, covered balcony, raised ceilings, Very nice circle drive provides extra parking. GPISD is an open school district allowing for school flexibility.
This property is eligible for a below market interest rate if the buyer meets traditional eligibility guidelines.
